OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly morning cloud and mist
OL,6,Fcould allow for the odd spot of
OL,7,Fdrizzle, but saying dry for most.
OL,8,FCloud then breaks to give some warm
OL,9,Fsunny spells by the afternoon, but
OL,10,Fstaying rather cloudy near coasts.
OL,11,FWinds will remain light.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA fine and dry evening for
OL,14,Fmost but with cloud along the coasts.
OL,15,FCloud builds inland overnight with
OL,16,Fpatchy coastal drizzle possible. Light
OL,17,Fnortherly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
