OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FCloudy with patchy drizzle
OL,6,Fpossible through the morning. Sunny
OL,7,Fspells developing later in the
OL,8,Fafternoon and into the evening. Light
OL,9,Fnortherly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FA fine
OL,12,Fand dry day on Sunday with northerly
OL,13,Fwinds. Cloudier through Monday and
OL,14,FTuesday with potential for patchy rain
OL,15,Fat times and light northerly winds.
